AttributeFile Attribute Modifier Plug-in
========================================

The AttributeFile Attribute Modifier Plug-in (AMP) implements the same feature
as the AttributeFile node. It parses a file with attribute information
associated with scene graph locations and adds those attributes to those
locations.

Environment Variables
---------------------

BOOST_HOME   The root of the boost directory.
KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/AttributeFile.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a
   Katana resources path.
